posting_body: ['SURROUNDED BY NATURAL CREEKS AND SERENE WOODED AREAS.', 'Newly built 3- and 4-bedroom homes for rent are available now in Conroe!', ' Brand-new rental homes are pet-friendly and include two-car garage, well-equipped spacious kitchen with pantry, walk-in closets, and washer / dryer connections.', 'The neighborhood is surrounded by natural creeks and serene wooded areas while still providing easy access to I-45, I-69, and downtown Conroe.', 'Up to $750 off upfront - Brand New Single-Family Homes - Pet-Friendly - Covered Patios - 2-Car Garage - Walk-in Closets - Spacious Fenced in Backyard - Regular Lawn Maintenance Included - Cable-Ready - Ceiling Fans - Central Air & Heating - Dishwasher & Microwave - Convenient Pantry - Vaulted Ceilings - Washer and Dryer Connections -', 'Up to $750 off for ASAP Move in', 'Contact me to schedule your appointment to view these beautiful, new homes', 'Mary Kay Noone, Agent', 'Apartment Living Locators', 'show contact info', 'Always a Free Service', '<URL>', '<URL>']
